  <brief_title>Thorax Computed Tomography Severity Score and Outcome in COVID-19 Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Initial Thoracic CT Findings and Mechanical Ventilation Requirement in Patients Admitted to Intensive Care Unit With COVID-19</official_title>
